                <h2>Charging times</h2>

<ul>
	<li>Congestion Charge: No charge 18:00-07:00 on weekdays or on weekends, public holidays or any days between Christmas Day and New Year's Day</li>
	<li>ULEZ and LEZ: Operate midnight to midnight, every day of the year</li>
</ul>

<p>Find out&nbsp;more about paying the <a href="/modes/driving/congestion-charge/paying-the-congestion-charge">Congestion Charge</a>, <a href="/modes/driving/ultra-low-emission-zone/ulez-payments">ULEZ</a> and <a href="/modes/driving/low-emission-zone/make-a-payment">LEZ</a>.</p>
